st week.=E2=80=9D (Gibbs previously declined to comment.) <br/><br/></li><l=
i><i>Roundball Rock</i>: A good source texted the other day with a suggesti=
on
worth considering. =E2=80=9CWould NBC use the NBA as the lead-out to next y=
ear=E2=80=99s Super Bowl? It makes a ton of sense.=E2=80=9D In the middle o=
f its first season with the NBA, NBC will produce the Super Bowl on Februar=
y 8, 2026, from Santa Clara, California.<br/><br/>Networks have generally u=
sed the post-Super Bowl time slot to promote entertainment or game show pro=
gramming. Given the $2.5 billion annual investment NBC is making on the NBA=
