=80=94think <b>LeBron James </b>and the Lakers against <b>Steph Curry</b> a=
nd the Warriors=E2=80=94coming out of the Super Bowl? That game certainly w=
ould set a record as the most viewed regular season game.<br/><br/>Would th=
e NFL allow a network to promote a rival league coming out of its biggest g=
ame? And, if NBC puts an NBA game in that window, would ABC schedule anothe=
r sport in that window the following year, or CBS the year after? We=E2=80=
=99re still two full NFL seasons away from any
answers to those questions, but it=E2=80=99s fun to think about.<br/></li><=
